WEBVTT

00:00:10.494 --> 00:00:20.494
There is a self-driven power inside us which
is called the Autonomous Nervous System
in English.

00:00:21.824 --> 00:00:39.784
It's located subtly in the medulla oblongata,
inside the spinal cord in our back.

00:00:40.767 --> 00:00:52.767
I told you that these are the three subtle powers
which make our Autonomous Nervous System work.

00:00:53.072 --> 00:01:08.992
Those two powers which are on the left and right,
one is called Ida and the other Pingala and
the one in the middle is called Sushumna.

00:01:09.026 --> 00:01:19.801
They are the three channels and the three powers
on these three channels are namely,
the one on the left side

00:01:19.801 --> 00:01:27.464
is Mahakali, the one on the right is Mahasaraswati
and the one in the middle is Mahalakshmi.

00:01:27.697 --> 00:01:38.157
Our existence and dissolution is due to Mahakali
Shakti, our body is formed by Mahasaraswati

00:01:38.413 --> 00:01:45.953
as well as all our thinking work/thought process
- whatever suggestions we have for the future,
whatever planning we do,

00:01:45.953 --> 00:01:52.313
we think, we implement, whatever
creative capacities we have,

00:01:52.313 --> 00:02:01.176
are all displayed and manifested through it.
And the power in between

00:02:01.402 --> 00:02:09.982
which we call the power of Mahalakshmi,
in which the people of this city of Bombay
believe very much,

00:02:09.982 --> 00:02:17.351
it is through this Mahalakshmi power that
our evolution takes place.

00:02:17.351 --> 00:02:23.286
We have evolved from amoeba to the human
form today because of this power only.

00:02:23.286 --> 00:02:29.716
Because of this power we sustain ourselves;
Dhaarana means to sustain.

00:02:30.626 --> 00:02:43.466
The qualities of every single substance, as I
told you yesterday that carbon has four valencies,
the nature of every single substance,

00:02:43.532 --> 00:02:54.932
or it's, what we say, properties all come through
this power and the sustenance of religion in a
human being is also due to this.

00:02:55.065 --> 00:03:00.565
A human being does also have some religion/attributes of
his own, otherwise why would he be called a human being?

00:03:00.712 --> 00:03:10.472
He has ten attributes/virtues, which can in a simpler
way be said, that the Ten Commandments in
the Bible are those ten virtues.

00:03:10.982 --> 00:03:18.912
These ten dharmas have many more subtle forms
about which we have mention in our scriptures
since ancient times.

00:03:18.912 --> 00:03:23.392
Many saints and sages found out
and have written a lot on it.

00:03:23.392 --> 00:03:31.990
The last thing I was telling you yesterday about
Dharma, because while describing the three Chakras,

00:03:31.993 --> 00:03:44.113
when we came to the navel chakra, I said that
Lakshmiji has a very close connection with
dharma because religion is in our stomach.

00:03:46.362 --> 00:03:51.562
Religion is not in the thought/mind. The person who
practices religion with the mind is not religious.

00:03:51.677 --> 00:03:58.317
Religion is not through thoughts, it is
in our stomach. Like, I tell you a simple thing,

00:03:58.317 --> 00:04:02.395
that if there is a truly religious man, that is,
one who should be called a realized soul -

00:04:02.395 --> 00:04:07.766
I don't consider that person religious who walks
around with a big mark or badge but one who is a
dedicated person from within,

00:04:07.766 --> 00:04:14.196
one who has become one with God, who is a
Yogi in the true sense, who is a realized soul,

00:04:14.478 --> 00:04:22.108
if that person goes to the house of someone
who has committed murder and harassed people,

00:04:22.108 --> 00:04:27.730
as soon as he eats food at that man's house, he
will start vomiting. He will not be able to bear it.

00:04:29.005 --> 00:04:34.125
He will not be able to see any naked woman.
As soon as he sees her, he will feel
like vomiting.

00:04:34.125 --> 00:04:36.618
His stomach won't be able to bear it.

00:04:36.982 --> 00:04:42.022
There must be many people among you who can't
even eat food at someone else's house.

00:04:42.022 --> 00:04:45.294
Going to their houses, they will
definitely feel like vomiting.

00:04:45.294 --> 00:04:52.245
No one can tell the reason for this. The simple reason
is that your religion[dharma] is not compatible
with the religion which is in that house.

00:04:54.445 --> 00:05:01.875
You may also have experienced many such
things in your life for which you might
not have found the answer.

00:05:01.875 --> 00:05:06.650
When our Dharma becomes weak or
when man's Dharma starts declining,

00:05:06.650 --> 00:05:13.430
the moment his religion starts declining,
gradually he starts compromising with life.

00:05:13.430 --> 00:05:17.512
When his compromise begins, he gradually
becomes weak.

00:05:17.512 --> 00:05:24.810
As soon as he becomes weak, sometimes some
evil spirits also come upon him.
Sometimes he himself becomes a evil spirit.

00:05:24.810 --> 00:05:29.003
When man falls from Dharma, he can only
descend into the devilish/subhuman form.

00:05:29.651 --> 00:05:37.901
Because now he can neither be born as an
animal nor can he be born as a deity.

00:05:39.114 --> 00:05:44.084
So being a human when he falls/strays from
his religion then where will he go?

00:05:44.239 --> 00:05:49.169
He has to go to the demonic form or
he has to go to the state of Hell.

00:05:49.169 --> 00:05:55.075
Now whether Hell exists or not, is there
any proof of this or not, what is it's proof,
Mataji please show us scientifically.

00:05:55.075 --> 00:06:00.256
So that cannot be done, but yes, for sure it is,
that I showed it to you even today morning

00:06:00.256 --> 00:06:03.787
and yesterday too, I showed you the pulsation
of the Kundalini, which you can see.

00:06:03.939 --> 00:06:10.819
You can see the pulsation of the Kundalini
with your own eyes, even though you have
not been realized yet.

00:06:10.819 --> 00:06:16.161
And those who have been realized have also
experienced the peace about which I am talking,

00:06:16.161 --> 00:06:21.336
that thoughtlessness where a person becomes
silent and within him all his thoughts stop

00:06:21.336 --> 00:06:26.161
and he becomes a witness and starts watching.
This happening takes place.

00:06:26.291 --> 00:06:30.991
What scientific proof can be given
for what happens inside you?

00:06:30.991 --> 00:06:35.134
Suppose you are listening to some nice,
beautiful music and you say you are enjoying it

00:06:35.134 --> 00:06:38.203
give some scientific proof for this,
then how can it be given?

00:06:38.203 --> 00:06:45.733
You become, this happens within you, and
cool vibrations start flowing through you.

00:06:45.733 --> 00:06:50.003
This happened to many among you yesterday
and you experienced it too

00:06:50.003 --> 00:06:55.494
and many people must have benefited from it
too and should move ahead in this.

00:06:56.642 --> 00:07:02.092
Those people who have understood this matter
deeply and have moved forward have reached
great heights today.

00:07:02.092 --> 00:07:06.251
While living in this world, they have become
superior to many sages and saints,

00:07:06.251 --> 00:07:11.322
and how many people they are giving realization,
and curing many of them also.

00:07:11.322 --> 00:07:19.645
Even diseases like cancer - we have a simple school
teacher here, he has cured cancer of so many people.

00:07:19.645 --> 00:07:24.165
And he is a very accomplished man,
although he is a very simple teacher.

00:07:24.165 --> 00:07:29.713
He has reached great heights and in Kundalini Shastra,
he is absolutely very [wise and] knowledgeable.

00:07:29.713 --> 00:07:37.785
He has acquired so much knowledge about Kundalini
Shastra that you'll be surprised as to where
this man has gained so much knowledge from.

00:07:37.785 --> 00:07:44.215
You have not known anything till now. When you
start knowing, then whatever deep/profound knowledge
there is,

00:07:44.215 --> 00:07:48.565
everything starts flowing from within because
first there must be the power to know.

00:07:48.565 --> 00:07:54.094
One who doesn't have the power to know - if you
do not have the power to listen, then how
will you understand what I am saying.

00:07:54.094 --> 00:07:58.278
If you don't have the power to see, then how
will you be able to see what I'm showing you?

00:07:58.278 --> 00:08:03.708
Therefore this cannot happen without your
consciousness becoming subtle first.

00:08:03.708 --> 00:08:09.548
Yesterday a gentleman came and told me,
"My brother's sickness, one of your
disciples was not able to cure,"

00:08:09.548 --> 00:08:17.971
and I have no faith in You," So I said,
"If you don't even have any faith in Me,
then what brought you here?"

00:08:17.971 --> 00:08:24.092
"If I cure your brother, you will have
faith in Me; What compulsion is this."

00:08:24.152 --> 00:08:31.602
"I have not taken any money from you, what
right do you have over Me, that you can
tell Me, 'I should cure your brother.'"

00:08:31.602 --> 00:08:39.035
You are saying to Me with so much authority,
" Awaken my Kundalini," so what
right do you have after all?

00:08:39.035 --> 00:08:44.875
Your right is that you have accepted Me
as your Mother, you have faith in Me,

00:08:44.965 --> 00:08:49.225
otherwise, I have nothing to take from
you, nor can you give Me anything.

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:55.559
But if you don't have faith at all, then
you just think, all these Deities sitting
on the chakras,

00:08:55.559 --> 00:09:01.322
will they accept the fact that you have absolutely
no faith in Me, no faith in these Gods,

00:09:01.322 --> 00:09:06.556
you don't have faith in God, you abuse
everyone morning-evening, and
will they run around and work for you?

00:09:07.659 --> 00:09:14.849
If there is an ordinary officer, then he
has so much protocol, then how much
protocol will that God Almighty have!

00:09:15.623 --> 00:09:20.573
We have become so egoistic that we think
that, "Our Kundalini should be awakened,

00:09:20.573 --> 00:09:26.610
this should happen for us, that should happen
for us, and we have absolutely no faith in God,
we are big shots," - so be where you are.

00:09:26.830 --> 00:09:31.130
It is very difficult for such people to get
realization. Let me tell you before hand.

00:09:31.153 --> 00:09:37.873
It is important that you come with faith.
Farmers have a lot of faith.

00:09:37.873 --> 00:09:45.688
I had gone to Rahuri, I was surprised thousands
of people had come; Crowds of five-five, six-six
thousand were getting realization just like that.

00:09:45.688 --> 00:09:50.417
(UNCLEAR) was saying, "What kind of sons of
Mother Earth are they, how quickly they
are getting it."

00:09:50.417 --> 00:09:55.958
There were some educated people, some
rich people too - it was not that they
were all completely illiterate -

00:09:55.958 --> 00:09:59.341
there were some illiterate people too,
but everyone was getting realization very quickly.

00:09:59.341 --> 00:10:03.604
So I asked them, "What is the matter?" They said,
"Mother, we have great reverence for You."

00:10:03.604 --> 00:10:08.370
So I asked, "Why do you have faith?"
They replied, "We do have. We are farming people."

00:10:08.370 --> 00:10:13.215
"How can we do farming without faith?
Farming cannot be done without faith."

00:10:13.575 --> 00:10:18.455
It is correct. Farming can't be done without faith.

00:10:18.524 --> 00:10:23.554
When a man thinks about how the
land/earth makes a seed grow,

00:10:23.554 --> 00:10:28.798
on her own She gives us so many fruits
and doesn’t want us to give her anything.

00:10:28.810 --> 00:10:35.710
Seeing it, man is certainly amazed and realizes
what a great miracle it is, what a great wonder it is!

00:10:35.710 --> 00:10:39.958
And when we go to the market here and
buy things, we take it for granted.

00:10:39.958 --> 00:10:44.460
We don't feel that something special
is happening or is a miracle.

00:10:46.684 --> 00:10:55.434
Having faith in God is a natural thing,
very natural, because whatever we have got,

00:10:55.434 --> 00:10:59.632
just think; today we have become human beings
from an amoeba, we have not evolved on our own.

00:10:59.632 --> 00:11:05.193
God Himself has incarnated in the world many times.
- He took ten incarnations in the world

00:11:05.193 --> 00:11:10.774
and in those ten Incarnations, He has worked very
hard in every Incarnation and has helped you people

00:11:10.774 --> 00:11:15.745
to reach to this state. This is correct. Whether
it is or not we will later make you realize.

00:11:15.745 --> 00:11:20.579
We told you yesterday itself that as a
scientist, you just keep your minds open.

00:11:20.579 --> 00:11:23.754
After that we will show you each and every thing.

00:11:24.342 --> 00:11:30.192
Before such an Almighty God we must come
with our heads bowed down.

00:11:30.192 --> 00:11:33.758
The person who thinks himself to be higher
than God should stay at his place.

00:11:33.758 --> 00:11:38.199
But he is in one sense. God has made
man higher than Himself.

00:11:38.199 --> 00:11:43.742
This is true in one sense, where even God
is at a loss and I also am.

00:11:43.742 --> 00:11:50.664
That is, God has given you freedom.
You have to choose your own evolution

00:11:50.664 --> 00:11:56.554
when you come to the level of a human being,
upon reaching this plane, you will have
to search it in your freedom.

00:11:56.554 --> 00:12:00.775
We cannot force you, that if we want we enchant you,

00:12:00.775 --> 00:12:06.841
that we make you unconscious, that we put
you in a trance, that we befool you,
it cannot happen like this.

00:12:06.841 --> 00:12:14.805
You have to choose it, you have to take this
decision in full consciousness, in full awareness,

00:12:14.805 --> 00:12:22.589
this has to be accepted that, 'Yes, I am going to
go on the path of God, I want to know the
power of God.' Only then will it happen.

00:12:22.757 --> 00:12:32.147
In this sense you are the highest. This
question does not arise in other creatures,
this question is of human beings.

00:12:32.147 --> 00:12:37.712
And that is why God bows down before man
bcause his evolution, his development,

00:12:37.712 --> 00:12:41.114
on reaching this state, just can't
happen without freedom.

00:12:41.114 --> 00:12:45.864
Because if I want to make you kings, then
only in your freedom can I make you kings.

00:12:45.864 --> 00:12:52.203
If you yourself are dependent, and if
you are doing something because of Me,
then how can we make you a king.

00:12:53.218 --> 00:13:02.138
This is the greatest liberation, the greatest freedom,
and for the greatest liberation, first the
intellect of man must be somewhat free.

00:13:02.138 --> 00:13:06.388
His decision should be made freely.
Every person should in complete freedom

00:13:06.388 --> 00:13:14.461
must accept that, 'Yes, we want this.'
Absolute faith means absolute freedom.

