Yesterday I told you about the three chakras
- today many new people have come -

00:13:24.144 --> 00:13:31.444
and among them I told that Mooladhara Chakra
is at the bottom. It contains the power
of Shri Ganesha, which is Eternal Childhood.

00:13:31.444 --> 00:13:38.812
And the important point of this I told is
that the Mooladhar, which is of
The Goddess, of Gauriji,

00:13:38.812 --> 00:13:48.816
