anything regarding this.

00:14:09.344 --> 00:14:12.212
They are innocent, they have innocence.

00:14:12.212 --> 00:14:18.837
Sex has no role to play in the Kundalini
awakening or in the evolution of humans.

00:14:18.837 --> 00:14:30.501
