00:14:44.873 --> 00:14:53.243
And he should have thoughts towards Her like
an extremely pure child, just like
Shri Ganesha had towards Gauri Ji.

00:14:53.601 --> 00:14:58.591
Later on, Tantrikas came to our
country and negated the efforts/did the opposite.

