I told you about our second chakra,
Swadhisthana Chakra, through which
we do all our creative work

00:16:05.458 --> 00:16:15.773
and whose power is Saraswati. The third chakra, I told you
was of Lakshmi ji and Narayan, i.e. Vishnu ji.

00:16:17.397 --> 00:16:30.870
