in today's condition/stage is called Bhavsagar.

00:16:38.388 --> 00:16:43.174
It has many conditions, stages - in
this stage it is called Bhava Sagar.

00:16:43.537 --> 00:16:54.177
That is why we say that 'Make us cross the ocean of
illusion, save us from the ocean of illusion' - the
world is an ocean, whatever has happened, the ocean remains.

00:16:54.488 --> 00:17:03.668
In this ocean, this world in which we have
come and this world in which we are living,
this should be called Bhavasagar.

00:17:04.199 --> 00:17:14.159
