Hussain, the two sons of Fatima.

00:18:59.963 --> 00:19:05.605
Whether this is true or not, you
should test it again on Kundalini.

00:19:05.627 --> 00:19:13.497
Like, a Muslim doctor who lives in Iran,
came to Me in London and said to Me

00:19:13.497 --> 00:19:17.361
