by imbalance - cancer is always caused by imbalance."

00:19:31.777 --> 00:19:40.567
This feeling is so strong and deeply embedded within
you that Mohammed Saheb is the only Incarnation
and can't there be other incarnations of Him?

00:19:40.567 --> 00:19:45.383
