of Dattatreya, I can cure you."

00:20:03.544 --> 00:20:08.362
At first that Muslim gentleman got very
angry, he went away, annoyed with Me.

00:20:08.362 --> 00:20:12.116
After that - but cancer is such a
disease that what to do -

00:20:12.116 --> 00:20:15.539
