Mother, I am ready to do whatever You say."

00:20:15.539 --> 00:20:22.114
Now his health is fine, because
Dattatreya Himself cannot accept this

00:20:22.114 --> 00:20:25.034
that why are we dividing Him into
so many divisions?

00:20:25.153 --> 00:20:30.053
Man wants to divide himself in this way.
God does not want to divide Himself.

00:20:30.122 --> 00:20:35.262
Man wants that, 'I am a Muslim, I am a Hindu'
- this is disgusting for God.

00:20:36.028 --> 00:20:42.678
It's weird to say, 'I am the nose, I am the eye,
I am the ear.' - to talk stupidly like that.

00:20:43.212 --> 00:20:49.782
God has created man in the whole universe;
Not to mould him into different shapes.

00:20:49.782 --> 00:20:55.806
There are many flowers blooming on the same tree.
After taking those flowers and plucking them,

00:20:55.806 --> 00:21:00.191
after killing them you people are fighting amongst
yourselves that, 'This religion is different,
that religion is different.'

