Just yesterday a gentleman had come from
Delhi – let me tell you his story.

00:21:05.232 --> 00:21:10.522
He too is in a lot of problem; he is realized
but he said, "This void of mine,"

00:21:10.522 --> 00:21:15.179
what we call the void, Bhavasagar, "Is caught."
I said, I asked him many things.

00:21:15.179 --> 00:21:19.140
I said, "Is this your problem, is that yours?"
He said, "No," I said, "Are you a Jan Sanghi?"

00:21:19.140 --> 00:21:24.817
