You forget to be bored. The joy in your
heart starts becoming so intense that
you forget this thing altogether.

00:42:26.785 --> 00:42:33.365
That's why I don't tell anyone but it
happens, automatically it happens.

00:42:36.847 --> 00:42:46.867
After that you'll see that the chakra above
is called the heart chakra, in this
heart chakra Jagdamba resides.

00:42:47.567 --> 00:42:58.047
You know Jagdamba Ji is Shiva, Shri Shiv's
consort. Shri Shiv resides in the heart.
Shiva resides in everyone's heart.

00:42:58.047 --> 00:43:04.554
The spark of the Spirit is inside our hearts,
which is the reflection of God Almighty.

00:43:04.601 --> 00:43:18.821
Whether it is there or not, you see
later on. It is there. Inside this
reflective form, the Spirit form

00:43:22.475 --> 00:43:31.825
is a light, like a flame, which stays
in our heart and watches all our actions.

00:43:32.024 --> 00:43:39.664
It keeps watching us all the time, it
does not get involved anywhere, it's
just a witness, keeps watching.

00:43:40.674 --> 00:43:47.874
And the Kundalini which is kept in our
triangular bone records everything.

00:43:47.874 --> 00:43:55.332
Whatever it sees, our whatever action
the light of the Spirit knows, it watches

00:43:55.332 --> 00:44:01.496
It knows our every action - we can't hide
anything from it. It's a witness, keeps watching.

00:44:01.944 --> 00:44:09.684
Like a reporter, and all it's light
keeps falling on the Kundalini and
the Kundalini keeps knowing.

00:44:09.684 --> 00:44:19.022
There is a triangle formed from the
heart to here. Above the forehead
is the seat of Shri Sadashiva.

00:44:19.022 --> 00:44:27.155
From there, the information goes to the Kundalini
and just like a tape recorder,
the Kundalini keeps noting down everything.

00:44:27.155 --> 00:44:31.671
Many people, sometimes [when] I ask them
something, they ask with great surprise,
"Mataji, how do you know?"

00:44:31.961 --> 00:44:37.601
So I know about you from your Kundalini,
I can play the whole tape. Just
played your tape - finished/done.

00:44:37.601 --> 00:44:41.578
And whatever I want - don't even have
to pull the tape - everything is revealed.

00:44:42.340 --> 00:44:50.120
Everything is stored in the Kundalini
and this flame of the Spirit keeps
burning alone, lonely.

00:44:51.075 --> 00:44:56.525
When the Kundalini is awakened, when the
Kundalini rises and pierces the
Bramharandhra, then

00:44:56.525 --> 00:45:02.422
The seat of Shri Sadashiva which is here
above the head, remains forever above
you all the time.

00:45:02.422 --> 00:45:09.252
Because of this you have the wisdom to
discriminate between truth and falsehood.
Conscience exists because of this.

00:45:09.252 --> 00:45:15.095
And then when it goes there and
touches it - it's like a small light
which keeps burning in the gas -

00:45:15.095 --> 00:45:20.326
and when the force of the gas comes
and mixes with it, then the whole
thing gets lit up.

00:45:20.326 --> 00:45:26.852
In the same way, the feeling comes into
your entire consciousness, it's awareness comes.

00:45:26.852 --> 00:45:31.499
The vibrations that come to your hands
later on are the effects of that consciousness.

00:45:34.166 --> 00:45:42.226
And only after that does a man become a
witness. This happening has to take place.

00:45:42.226 --> 00:45:47.518
This is not going to happen with any lecture.
Even now when I am giving you a speech,
My vibrations are still flowing

00:45:47.518 --> 00:45:51.347
and they are coming and the happening,
whatever it is, is taking place within you.

00:45:51.347 --> 00:45:56.893
But it doesn't work out with all those
people who give speeches and read books.

