00:46:38.651 --> 00:46:46.521
They were very ordinary Mothers, very
ordinary, but strong/powerful from within.

00:46:46.521 --> 00:46:50.714
People had to be Realized to know Their powers
otherwise people don't know it.

00:46:50.714 --> 00:46:57.009
In Sitaji's time, people were so sensitive,
they were quite sensitive - today such
a thing can't be seen.

00:46:57.009 --> 00:47:00.994
I had just been to Satara and I realised that
the people of that sensitivity are here.

00:47:00.994 --> 00:47:06.764
Otherwise I have never seen such anywhere else
who seemed to know exactly what the thing is.

00:47:06.883 --> 00:47:13.923
They were such sensitive people that they got
realized in no time. Their king's mother
was so sensitive that I was very surprised.

00:47:13.923 --> 00:47:18.569
I said, 'In a small place like Satara -
this might there due to the virtuous deeds
of Shivaji -

00:47:18.569 --> 00:47:24.763
but people were so sensitive as if the lamps
were fully ready and thus they lit instantly.

00:47:24.763 --> 00:47:30.692
Instantly - so very beautiful! When such
people are there, this work gets done.

00:47:30.692 --> 00:47:37.679
There must be sensitivity for this thing,
that a person is sensitive. Otherwise,
I work hard and have done it.

