Now, among the upper Chakras, that I
have told, the Chakra of Jagdamba,

00:47:41.802 --> 00:47:46.234
You know that Jagdamba ji many times
after incarnating came to the
Bhavasagara [ocean of existence]

00:47:46.234 --> 00:47:54.482
and has protected all Her devotees; you too
are among them. Today in Kaliyuga,
you are searching for the same.

00:47:54.482 --> 00:47:59.751
You too have come from among them. Without
you having some assets, you would not have
come and would not get realization.

