00:48:18.058 --> 00:48:23.285
Will give it to whosoever is authorized and
whatever I can do, how much I can put

00:48:23.285 --> 00:48:26.045
with the power of My love, I will.

00:48:26.045 --> 00:48:29.636
It happens, has happened to many, and has
happened to thousands and should happen
to you too.

00:48:30.686 --> 00:48:38.046
Now above that, the Chakra that is on it's
side, you can say that it is the Chakra
of Shri Ram and Sita

00:48:38.046 --> 00:48:45.291
because in evolution when He incarnated
ten times, one of those incarnations
was of Shri Ram and Sita.

00:48:45.291 --> 00:48:50.996
