Now the above Agnya Chakra, which I had told,
has the incarnation of MahaVishnu in it.
If you read Devi Bhagavat,

00:50:48.365 --> 00:50:56.336
then you will know that MahaVishnu
is a very big incarnation of the Son.

00:50:56.336 --> 00:51:02.286
And in that he has considered Shri Ganesha
as the main principle. Considering
Shri Ganesha as the main principle

00:51:02.286 --> 00:51:06.384
that incarnation was sent into the world,
whose name is Jesus Christ.

00:51:06.384 --> 00:51:13.154
Jesus Christ is none other but the incarnation
of Shri Mahavishnu, whom we call Bauddha.

00:51:13.154 --> 00:51:18.929
He is the incarnation of Jesus Christ
and His mother was Radhaji Herself.

00:51:18.929 --> 00:51:24.689
It's evident that the name Jesus which they
have given, this name Jesu, is from Yashoda.

00:51:24.689 --> 00:51:28.624
Yashoda's name is not mentioned anywhere
so they have named Him Jesu

00:51:28.624 --> 00:51:34.566
and His name, which is Christ, is
from none other than Krishna,
because Krishna was His father.

00:51:34.693 --> 00:51:42.453
Repeatedly He describes His Father, you
should read Devi Mahatma, in Devi Mahatma
it is completely written about This Child.

00:51:42.453 --> 00:51:46.258
There is only a difference in the name.
It says MahaVishnu and His name is Jesus Christ.

00:51:46.258 --> 00:51:49.342
If you read them, you will know exactly
that these are His descriptions only.

00:51:49.342 --> 00:51:57.956
Fully it is His description that He came into
the world and the things He did and the way
He forgave; Forgiveness was His key principle.

00:51:57.956 --> 00:52:04.534
In forgiveness, whatever weapons there were
He dissolved them and put them into forgiveness.

00:52:04.534 --> 00:52:07.700
He has given forgiveness as the
greatest weapon that man has.

00:52:07.700 --> 00:52:13.922
Now the reality of this too, it's feeling,
of everything, you can realize through
Kundalini awakening

00:52:13.922 --> 00:52:19.048
that when the Kundalini rises and when it
stops at any Chakra, then the name of
that Deity has to be taken.

00:52:19.048 --> 00:52:22.556
