will not rise. You can see this yourself.

00:52:22.556 --> 00:52:26.760
When the Kundalini rises, gradually you will
notice that you will keep getting
vibrations on the chakras.

00:52:26.760 --> 00:52:30.699
You can also see it with your eyes.
There you will have to take the name of
that very Deity which I am saying.

00:52:30.699 --> 00:52:34.434
If you do not take the name then the Kundalini
will not rise and when the Kundalini rises

00:52:34.434 --> 00:52:37.479
you should know that the Deity there is happy.

00:52:37.479 --> 00:52:41.986
