considered to be the incarnation of Sahasrara.

00:52:41.986 --> 00:52:49.607
Kalki means, the One who is the master of all
the seven chakras, the master of all
the seven chakras is Kalki.

00:52:49.607 --> 00:52:55.485
And hence Her incarnation is believed
to be in Sahasrara and this is the
highest incarnation of Adi Shakti

00:52:55.485 --> 00:53:04.035
Because only due to this, because of Adi Shakti
only, Sahasrara can be opened here.
